484
00:23:28,907 --> 00:23:30,826
I promised the crowd
a floor show.

485
00:23:47,384 --> 00:23:49,261
No!

486
00:23:49,302 --> 00:23:51,513
You don't get to hurt my kids,

487
00:23:51,555 --> 00:23:54,182
shoot somebody in front of me
and leave without any payback.

488
00:23:54,641 --> 00:23:56,560
Dodgy,

489
00:23:56,601 --> 00:23:58,687
